The lecture of Dr. Ballhausen from @LMU_Muenchen is over. It has been very informative and inspiring. Hussar to our speaker! 

But his work day is not done, yet: Currently he is still engaged in  workshop organised by the medical faculty @unibielefeld. Tirelessly for science!
